{"tid":1311817,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"放閃就一定幸福？","createTime":"2019-07-13T10:55:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T17:46:01.000Z","uid":163639,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c9cb7cb3e1e32f1e219ccdf558546df061ea941e","tid":1311817,"uid":163639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T10:55:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jfMzF03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjfMzF03.jpg&h=a1d4bb2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n幸福的感覺不是由放閃而來，而是兩顆生命的結連與交流。<br />\n<br />\n經常煩惱周未拍拖節目？你會覺得累嗎？看電影、吃飯、逛街重覆又重覆，你會覺得悶嗎？<br />\n<br />\n究竟什麼是拍拖？拍就是兩者靠近，拖就是雙方連結，我想拍拖就是兩個人一起交流和編織生命的故事。所以拍拖的重點不在於節目，而是在於雙方。很多時候看到很多情侶，只有拍，沒有拖，只靠不停的放閃，從外界裡偷取短暫的快慰。<br />\n<br />\n幸福不是一起看電影、尋找眼球上的刺激，而是大家事後對電影的看法討論、人性的探討；<br />\n<br />\n幸福不是一起吃大餐、追求味蕾上的享受，而是藉著大家對食物的不同喜惡、互相交流；<br />\n<br />\n幸福可以是雙方坐在海旁，細說生活瑣碎事，因為你重要，一切瑣碎事在他眼中都是大事。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/Bz2rCgrBaFg/?igshid=1265x0ldum9w8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBz2rCgrBaFg%2F%3Figshid%3D1265x0ldum9w8&d=ev%2BvVaAtQ3cORw7W3wlzWZvkp%2FM1ZBOvf84g0fLsyFs%3D&h=adfbdfe6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBz2rCgrBaFg%2F%3Figshid%3D1265x0ldum9w8&h=0a8a61f3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/Bz2rCgrBaFg/?igshid=1265x0ldum9w8</a>"},{"pid":"ebc262c1b90348ed319e270ed2b0de68c4635091","tid":1311817,"uid":274246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T11:19:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b6ce687310f1409c54b0c883f3496a8fa3bae64","tid":1311817,"uid":201604,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T11:21:52.000Z","msg":"幸福過冇得放"},{"pid":"2023b47cd253589ef2ed7219256822dc987823ab","tid":1311817,"uid":208973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b6ce687310f1409c54b0c883f3496a8fa3bae64","tid":1311817,"uid":201604,"li